Devoted Spirit (Stance) [Law]
Level: Crusader 6, Saint 6
Prerequisite: Two Devoted Spirit maneuvers
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Stance

This stance allows you to treat a potential d20 result as an 11. You use this ability immediately when rolling a d20. You use this ability once per round on either an attack roll or a saving throw. Using this ability does not take an action.  Additionally, while this ability has not be exercised, you gain a bonus to all skills equal to your Charisma modifier, if any.
